    <item>
      <title>5 Tips for Writing Technical Blog Posts That People Actually Read</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/writing-1-blogging-tips/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/writing-1-blogging-tips/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Technical writing doesn&amp;rsquo;t have to be dry and boring. Here&amp;rsquo;s how to create blog posts that educate and engage your audience.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;1-start-with-a-hook&#34;&gt;1. Start with a Hook&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Your opening paragraph should answer: &amp;ldquo;Why should I care?&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#39;callout callout-tip&#39;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;callout-inner&#34;&gt;&#xA;    ðŸ’¡ Tip: Lead with a problem your reader faces, then promise a solution.&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bad opening&lt;/strong&gt;: &amp;ldquo;In this post, I will explain how to use React hooks.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Good opening&lt;/strong&gt;: &amp;ldquo;Tired of wrestling with class components and &lt;code&gt;this&lt;/code&gt; binding? React hooks make state management cleaner and your code easier to understand.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Markdown for Technical Writers: A Comprehensive Guide</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/writing-2-markdown-guide/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/writing-2-markdown-guide/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Markdown is the lingua franca of technical writing. Whether you&amp;rsquo;re writing blog posts, README files, or documentation, mastering Markdown is essential.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;why-markdown&#34;&gt;Why Markdown?&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Simple syntax&lt;/strong&gt; - Easy to learn and write&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Platform independent&lt;/strong&gt; - Works everywhere (GitHub, Hugo, Jekyll, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Version control friendly&lt;/strong&gt; - Plain text, perfect for Git&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Widely supported&lt;/strong&gt; - Most dev tools support it&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;basic-syntax&#34;&gt;Basic Syntax&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;headers&#34;&gt;Headers&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-markdown&#34; data-lang=&#34;markdown&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;# H1 - Main title&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;## H2 - Section&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;### H3 - Subsection&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;#### H4 - Sub-subsection&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;emphasis&#34;&gt;Emphasis&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-markdown&#34; data-lang=&#34;markdown&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;*italic* or &lt;span style=&#34;font-style:italic&#34;&gt;_italic_&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;**bold**&lt;/span&gt; or &lt;span style=&#34;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;__bold__&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-style:italic&#34;&gt;**&lt;/span&gt;*bold italic*** or &lt;span style=&#34;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;___bold italic___&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;~~strikethrough~~&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Result: &lt;em&gt;italic&lt;/em&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;bold&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;bold italic&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;, &lt;del&gt;strikethrough&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
